<h2>POAP2RSS has been retired</h2>

<p>On July 31, 2026, the creators of <a href="https://poap.xyz">POAP</a> (the Proof of Attendance Protocol) wound down the platform. Because <strong>POAP2RSS</strong> worked entirely by reading live POAP claim activity through the POAP API, it stopped working when that API went offline, and the service has now been retired.</p>

<p>Thank you to everyone who used POAP2RSS to follow drops and collectors over the years. It was a joy to build something on top of POAP, and a small sadness to see it go.</p>

<h3>Looking for POAP history?</h3>
<p>Historical POAP data — drops, artwork, and addresses — is being preserved by the POAP team at <a href="https://poaparchive.com">poaparchive.com</a>.</p>

<p><small>With gratitude to Isabel, Patricio, and the whole POAP team. — Jamie</small></p>
